Installing SWAML
****************

Short Answer:
-------------

	make install


Long Answer:
------------

Dependencies:

	- python >= 2.4.0
	- python-rdflib >= 2.3.1
	- python-xml >= 0.8.4
	- python-urljr >= 1.0.1
        
As root user you may run:

	make install
	
This command will install SWAML at common directories. Then it'll be available
a new command: 'swaml'.

To uninstall it's also easy:

	make uninstall

